sentence: Cumulative risk curves (Figure 1A and B) demonstrated a 2.7% risk of first skin cancer treatment at 2 years after a first transplant code in Optum, and 12.4% in MarketScan.

The risk of having 10 or more skin cancers treated was approximately 3% in Optum and 7% in MarketScan at 2 years after the first skin cancer treatment encounter (Figure 2).
